        "subject": "LU-19875 o2iblnd: drain conns before FMR/FastReg pool release",
        "message": "LU-19875 o2iblnd: drain conns before FMR/FastReg pool release\n\nFMR/FastReg pools teardown should happen after all connections\nare gone, because the pools are tied to TX/conn completion.\nExecute the pools teardown routine after conns have drained.\n\nLustre-change: https://review.whamcloud.com/63985\nLustre-commit: 6586be4f72fcef6ddd5e71ebeb62e3de651163e9\n\nTest-Parameters: trivial testlist=sanity-lnet\nSigned-off-by: Serguei Smirnov <ssmirnov@whamcloud.com>\nChange-Id: I0d557f5465d644a3b8934c3f20f66f43d6686d59\nReviewed-by: Xinxia Qu <xqu@ddn.com>\nReviewed-by: Chris Horn <chris.horn@hpe.com>\nSigned-off-by: Etienne AUJAMES <eaujames@ddn.com>\n"
